<div class="content-h1"><h1>Sariel</h1></div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="place">
<p id="openCatp" style="display:none">开放分类：<a href="//fenlei.baike.com/S%E5%BC%80%E5%A4%B4%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="S开头单词">S开头单词</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="天使">天使</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="宗教">宗教</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="英文单词">英文单词</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="英语">英语</a></p>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="information" id="unifyprompt"><div class="summary" id="anchor" name="anchor">
		请用一段简单的话描述该词条，马上<a action="editsummaryhref" href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="editSummary();return false;">添加摘要</a>。
		</div></div>
<input id="doctitle" name="doctitle" type="hidden" value="Sariel"/><div id="hd_ad_doc_109"> </div>
<div id="float_section" style="display:none;">
<div class="catalog">
<div class="full-list">
